text:
Hi Guys, I am using HubSpot form on a HubSpot page. I need to style the radio buttons on the form. Below is the code I added: if(event.data.type === 'hsFormCallback' &amp;&amp; event.data.eventName === 'onFormReady') {
    $('.hs-form-radio-display').click(function(){
         $(".hs-form-radio-display").css('background-color', 'white');
         $("input[type='radio']:checked").parent().css('background-color', 'blue');
     });
  }
